snippet: Rory McIlroy missed the cut for the third time in three tries at the Players Championship while Tiger Woods finished the day with a four-under 68.
abstract: Rory McIlroy misses the cut for the third time in three tries at the Players Championship while Tiger Woods finishes the day with a four-under 68 to make the cut; Zach Johnson, Matt Kuchar and Kevin Na share second-round lead.
lead_paragraph: Rory McIlroy missed the cut for the third time in three tries at the Players Championship while Tiger Woods finished the day with a four-under 68.
